1. Kukavice se plaše mraka. (Cowards are afraid of the dark.)
2. Ne želim da budem kukavica i pobegnem. (I don't want to be a coward and run away.)
3. Kukavica je ostavila prijatelja na cedilu. (The coward abandoned their friend in a time of need.)
4. *Kukavice*, rekao je hrabrić, neće me sprečiti da uradim ono što je ispravno. ( "Cowards," said the brave one, "will not stop me from doing what is right.")
5. Ne možeš stalno biti kukavica i izbegavati odgovornost. (You can't always be a coward and avoid responsibility.)
6. Nemoj da budeš kukavica, suoči se sa svojim strahovima. (Don't be a coward, face your fears.)
7. *Kukavice* su ostale u pozadini, dok su hrabri ljudi išli napred. ("Cowards," stayed behind while brave people moved forward.)
8. On je kukavica, nikada se neće usuditi da kaže šta stvarno misli. (He's a coward, he'll never dare to say what he really thinks.)